t, pushing against the thin fabric of his cleats as he approached the starting block at lane six.\", \"from\": 371, \"to\": 523, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lindo\", \"from\": 371, \"to\": 376}, {\"ngram\": \"the rubber-coated turf\", \"from\": 388, \"to\": 410}, {\"ngram\": \"his feet\", \"from\": 419, \"to\": 427}, {\"ngram\": \"the thin fabric\", \"from\": 445, \"to\": 460}, {\"ngram\": \"his cleats\", \"from\": 464, \"to\": 474}, {\"ngram\": \"the starting block\", \"from\": 492, \"to\": 510}, {\"ngram\": \"lane\", \"from\": 514, \"to\": 518}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Before him stood 10 hurdles: metal frames spaced evenly across the track.\", \"from\": 525, \"to\": 598, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"10 hurdles\", \"from\": 542, \"to\": 552}, {\"ngram\": \"metal frames\", \"from\": 554, \"to\": 566}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 588, \"to\": 597}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If he could leap over each one - and do it quickly - he stood a chance of joining Canada's Olympic track and field team.\", \"from\": 599, \"to\": 719, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 681, \"end\": 687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999999994552127, \"rank\": 5.422599372110048e-10, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"each one\", \"from\": 621, \"to\": 629}, {\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 669}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If not, his Olympic dreams would be over for the year.\", \"from\": 720, \"to\": 774, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his Olympic dreams\", \"from\": 728, \"to\": 746}, {\"ngram\": \"the year\", \"from\": 765, \"to\": 773}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But there was a bigger obstacle weighing on Lindo's mind.\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 833, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bigger obstacle\", \"from\": 790, \"to\": 807}, {\"ngr