mming up public support for his appeal.\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1271, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The race\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1140}, {\"ngram\": \"his best shot\", \"from\": 1159, \"to\": 1172}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic squad\", \"from\": 1181, \"to\": 1198}, {\"ngram\": \"his best chance\", \"from\": 1210, \"to\": 1225}, {\"ngram\": \"public support\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1255}, {\"ngram\": \"his appeal\", \"from\": 1260, \"to\": 1270}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lindo and his family came to Canada in April 2019, on the heels of what they describe as yet another assassination attempt against his father, George Lindo.\", \"from\": 1275, \"to\": 1431, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1304, \"end\": 1310, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999999994552127, \"rank\": 5.422599372110048e-10, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lindo\", \"from\": 1275, \"to\": 1280}, {\"ngram\": \"his family\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1295}, {\"ngram\": \"April\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1319}, {\"ngram\": \"the heels\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1338}, {\"ngram\": \"yet another assassination attempt\", \"from\": 1364, \"to\": 1397}, {\"ngram\": \"his father\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1416}, {\"ngram\": \"George Lindo\", \"from\": 1418, \"to\": 1430}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The family was originally from Jamaica, a Caribbean island long roiled by political conflict.\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1526, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1464, \"end\": 1471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.704300704582667e-16, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The family\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1443}, {\"ngram\": \"a Caribbean island\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1491}, {\"ngram\": \"political conflict\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1525}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For decades, two parties had been fighting for dominance on the island: the right-leaning Jamaican Labour Party and its left-wing rival, the People's National Party.\", \"from\": 1528, \"to\": 1693, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1618, \"end\": 1639, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_Labour_Party\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jamaican Labour Party\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_Labour_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_Labour_Party\"}, {\"begin\": 1678, \"end\": 1692, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_National_Party\", \"score\": 0.9999999953315637, \"rank\": 4.668879614975448e-09, \"text\": \"National Party\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_National_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_National_Party\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"decades\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1539}, {\"ngram\": \"two parties\", \"from\": 1541, \"to\": 1552}, {\"ngram\": \"dominance\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1584}, {\"ngram\": \"the island\", \"from\": 1588, \"to\": 1598}, {\"ngram\": \"its left-wing rival\", \"from\": 1644, \"to\": 1663}]}, {\"sentence\": \"George, a political activist, was a volunteer for the latter - and that, Lindo explained, put him in the crosshairs.\", \"from\": 1695, \"to\": 1811, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"George\", \"from\": 1695, \"to\": 1701}, {\"ngram\": \"a political activist\", \"from\": 1703, \"to\": 1723}, {\"ngram\": \"a volunteer\", \"from\": 1729, \"to\": 1740}, {\"ngram\": \"the latter\", \"from\": 1745, \"to\": 1755}, {\"ngram\": \"Lindo\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1773}, {\"ngram\": \"the crosshairs\", \"from\": 1796, \"to\": 1810}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2012, George claims an assailant slashed his neck.\", \"from\": 1813, \"to\": 1866, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"George\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1828}, {\"ngram\": \"an assailant\", \"from\": 1836, \"to\": 1848}, {\"ngram\": \"his neck\", \"from\": 1857, \"to\": 1865}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2016, he said he narrowly avoided gunfire at a bar.\", \"from\": 1867, \"to\": 1921, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gunfire\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 1911}, {\"ngram\": \"a bar\", \"from\": 1915, \"to\": 1920}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And in 2019, two armed gunmen appeared to be stalking him.\", \"from\": 1922, \"to\": 1980, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two armed gunmen\", \"from\": 1935, \"to\": 1951}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have experienced a life that I never want my siblings to experience,\\\" said Lindo.\", \"from\": 1982, \"to\": 2066, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a life\", \"from\": 2002, \"to\": 2008}, {\"ngram\": \"my siblings\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2038}, {\"ngram\": \"experience\", \"from\": 2042, \"to\": 2052}, {\"ngram\": \"Lindo\", \"from\": 2060, \"to\": 2065}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now 20, he was only 15 years old when he, his parents and his younger siblings fled the country.\", \"from\": 2067, \"to\": 2163, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his parents\", \"from\": 2109, \"to\": 2120}, {\"ngram\": \"his younger siblings\", \"from\": 2125, \"to\": 2145}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 2151, \"to\": 2162}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They arrived in Toronto, the bustling capital of Ontario.\", \"from\": 2165, \"to\": 2222, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2181, \"end\": 2188, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\", \"score\": 0.9999999999881766, \"rank\": 1.1552180465892474e-11, \"text\": \"Toronto\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\"}, {\"begin\": 2214, \"end\": 2221, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ontario\", \"score\": 0.9999996962260873, \"rank\": 3.0377408907397116e-07, \"text\": \"Ontario\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ontario\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ontario\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But confronted with the complexities of a foreign immigration system, the family was unsure whether to hire a lawyer.\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2340, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the complexities\", \"from\": 2243, \"to\": 2259}, {\"ngram\": \"a foreign immigration system\", \"from\": 2263, \"to\": 2291}, {\"ngram\": \"the family\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2303}, {\"ngram\": \"a lawyer\", \"from\": 2331, \"to\": 2339}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They ultimately completed their asylum application without access to legal counsel.\", \"from\": 2341, \"to\": 2424, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their asylum application\", \"from\": 2367, \"to\": 2391}, {\"ngram\": \"access\", \"from\": 2400, \"to\": 2406}, {\"ngram\": \"legal counsel\", \"from\": 2410, \"to\": 2423}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2020, their application was denied.\", \"from\": 2426, \"to\": 2464, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their application\", \"from\": 2435, \"to\": 2452}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a statement released to the media outlet CTV, the Canadian government's immigration department cited a lack of \\\"documentary evidence to demonstrate that they are at risk of harm or persecution in Jamaica\\\".\", \"from\": 2465, \"to\": 2673, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2509, \"end\": 2512, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CTV_News\", \"score\": 0.9999941133101409, \"rank\": 5.88672452778821e-06, \"text\": \"CTV\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CTV_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CTV_News\"}, {\"begin\": 2518, \"end\": 2537, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_Canada\", \"score\": 0.9905979746581696, \"rank\": 0.009491262408638087, \"text\": \"Canadian government\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_Canada\"}, {\"begin\": 2664, \"end\": 2671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.704300704582667e-16, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 2468, \"to\": 2479}, {\"ngram\": \"a lack\", \"from\": 2569, \"to\": 2575}, {\"ngram\": \"documentary evidence\", \"from\": 2580, \"to\": 2600}, {\"ngram\": \"risk\", \"from\": 2633, \"to\": 2637}, {\"ngram\": \"harm\", \"from\": 2641, \"to\": 2645}, {\"ngram\": \"persecution\", \"from\": 2649, \"to\": 2660}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Lindo family has been living under the threat of deportation ever since.\", \"from\": 2675, \"to\": 2751, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Lindo family\", \"from\": 2675, \"to\": 2691}, {\"ngram\": \"the threat\", \"from\": 2714, \"to\": 2724}, {\"ngram\": \"deportation\", \"from\": 2728, \"to\": 2739}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Without a successful asylum claim, they became classified as undocumented under Canadian law.\", \"from\": 2752, \"to\": 2845, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2832, \"end\": 2844, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_of_Canada\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Canadian law\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_of_Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_of_Canada\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a successful asylum claim\", \"from\": 2760, \"to\": 2785}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Still, Lindo and his family started to put down roots in Canada.\", \"from\": 2849, \"to\": 2913, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2906, \"end\": 2912, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999999994552127, \"rank\": 5.422599372110048e-10, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lindo\", \"from\": 2856, \"to\": 2861}, {\"ngram\": \"his family\", \"from\": 2866, \"to\": 2876}, {\"ngram\": \"roots\", \"from\": 2897, \"to\": 2902}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lindo's youngest sister Tameliah was born in the country.\", \"from\": 2914, \"to\": 2971, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lindo's youngest sister\", \"from\": 2914, \"to\": 2937}, {\"ngram\": \"Tameliah\", \"from\": 2938, \"to\": 2946}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 2959, \"to\": 2970}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lindo himself completed high school and earned a scholarship as a student athlete, known for his ability to dart across the track.\", \"from\": 2972, \"to\": 3102, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lindo\", \"from\": 2972, \"to\": 2977}, {\"ngram\": \"high school\", \"from\": 2996, \"to\": 3007}, {\"ngram\": \"a scholarship\", \"from\": 3019, \"to\": 3032}, {\"ngram\": \"a student athlete\", \"from\": 3036, \"to\": 3053}, {\"ngram\": \"his ability\", \"from\": 3065, \"to\": 3076}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 3092, \"to\": 3101}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lindo had been competing in the 110-metre hurdles for as long as he can remember.\", \"from\": 3104, \"to\": 3185, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lindo\", \"from\": 3104, \"to\": 3109}, {\"ngram\": \"the 110-metre hurdles\", \"from\": 3132, \"to\": 3153}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it was only when he was 18 that he realised he could surpass other runners with more experience.\", \"from\": 3186, \"to\": 3286, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other runners\", \"from\": 3251, \"to\": 3264}, {\"ngram\": \"more experience\", \"from\": 3270, \"to\": 3285}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lindo was eventually taken under the wing of Charles Allen, a coach who had competed in the 2004 Athens Olympics.\", \"from\": 3288, \"to\": 3401, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3333, \"end\": 3346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_E._Allen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.661309820655211e-23, \"text\": \"Charles Allen\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_E._Allen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_E._Allen\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lindo\", \"from\": 3288, \"to\": 3293}, {\"ngram\": \"the wing\", \"from\": 3321, \"to\": 3329}, {\"ngram\": \"a coach\", \"from\": 3348, \"to\": 3355}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2004 Athens Olympics\", \"from\": 3376, \"to\": 3400}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They would often notice each other at the Toronto Track and Field Center, and Lindo approached the former Olympian - and coach with Canada's national team - about how to improve his technique.\", \"from\": 3403, \"to\": 3595, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3509, \"end\": 3517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0845694384671006e-13, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 3535, \"end\": 3541, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999999994552127, \"rank\": 5.422599372110048e-10, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Toronto Track and Field Center\", \"from\": 3441, \"to\": 3475}, {\"ngram\": \"Lindo\", \"from\": 3481, \"to\": 3486}, {\"ngram\": \"his technique\", \"from\": 3581, \"to\": 3594}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He used to see that I was training on my own,\\\" said Lindo.\", \"from\": 3597, \"to\": 3656, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lindo\", \"from\": 3650, \"to\": 3655}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He saw my potential and [said], the day I am serious about it, I know where to find him.\\\"\", \"from\": 3657, \"to\": 3747, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my potential\", \"from\": 3665, \"to\": 3677}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Under Allen's tutelage, Lindo began training with Canada's national track and field team, with the aim of qualifying for the 2024 Paris Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 3749, \"to\": 3899, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3755, \"end\": 3760, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_L._Allen\", \"score\": 0.7640756950550618, \"rank\": 0.30877085380880104, \"text\": \"Allen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_L._Allen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_L._Allen\"}, {\"begin\": 3799, \"end\": 3805, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999999994552127, \"rank\": 5.422599372110048e-10, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lindo\", \"from\": 3773, \"to\": 3778}, {\"ngram\": \"the aim\", \"from\": 3844, \"to\": 3851}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paris Olympic Games\", \"from\": 3870, \"to\": 3898}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lindo dreamed of becoming the first Canadian to score a medal in the 110-metre hurdles since Mark McKoy won gold at the 1992 Barcelona Olympics.\", \"from\": 3901, \"to\": 4045, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3937, \"end\": 3945, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9998285713881555, \"rank\": 0.0001714580042397662, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}, {\"begin\": 3994, \"end\": 4004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_McKoy\", \"score\": 1