rnaments, Lindo had to remain in Canada.\", \"from\": 4180, \"to\": 4285, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4278, \"end\": 4284, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999999994552127, \"rank\": 5.422599372110048e-10, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his teammates\", \"from\": 4193, \"to\": 4206}, {\"ngram\": \"international tournaments\", \"from\": 4228, \"to\": 4253}, {\"ngram\": \"Lindo\", \"from\": 4255, \"to\": 4260}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If he left, he feared his undocumented status would bar him from re-entering the country.\", \"from\": 4286, \"to\": 4375, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his undocumented status\", \"from\": 4308, \"to\": 4331}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 4363, \"to\": 4374}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a significant setback.\", \"from\": 4377, \"to\": 4406, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a significant setback\", \"from\": 4384, \"to\": 4405}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lindo explained that those foreign competitions could have helped him reach the threshold to earn a guaranteed spot on Canada's Olympic team.\", \"from\": 4407, \"to\": 4548, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4526, \"end\": 4532, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999999994552127, \"rank\": 5.422599372110048e-10, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lindo\", \"from\": 4407, \"to\": 4412}, {\"ngram\": \"those foreign competitions\", \"from\": 4428, \"to\": 4454}, {\"ngram\": \"the threshold\", \"from\": 4483, \"to\": 4496}, {\"ngram\": \"a guaranteed spot\", \"from\": 4505, \"to\": 4522}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nevertheless, his performances at Canadian track meets were strong enough to nab him a slot at the Olympic trials in Montreal, scheduled for the end of June.\", \"from\": 4550, \"to\": 4707, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4667, \"end\": 4675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montreal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.54666941400414e-21, \"text\": \"Montreal\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montreal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Montreal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his performances\", \"from\": 4564, \"to\": 4580}, {\"ngram\": \"a slot\", \"from\": 4635, \"to\": 4641}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic trials\", \"from\": 4645, \"to\": 4663}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 4691, \"to\": 4698}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 4702, \"to\": 4706}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was the first time I felt ready for a championship,\\\" said Lindo.\", \"from\": 4709, \"to\": 4777, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 4717, \"to\": 4731}, {\"ngram\": \"a championship\", \"from\": 4749, \"to\": 4763}, {\"ngram\": \"Lindo\", \"from\": 4771, \"to\": 4776}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the lead-up to the Olympic trials would prove to be a tumultuous time for Lindo.\", \"from\": 4781, \"to\": 4865, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the lead-up\", \"from\": 4785, \"to\": 4796}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic trials\", \"from\": 4800, \"to\": 4818}, {\"ngram\": \"a tumultuous time\", \"from\": 4837, \"to\": 4854}, {\"ngram\": \"Lindo\", \"from\": 4859, \"to\": 4864}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Over the years, he and his family had applied for every single legal avenue available for them to remain in Canada - but again and again, they were refused.\", \"from\": 4866, \"to\": 5022, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4974, \"end\": 4980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999999994552127, \"rank\": 5.422599372110048e-10, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the years\", \"from\": 4871, \"to\": 4880}, {\"ngram\": \"his family\", \"from\": 4889, \"to\": 4899}, {\"ngram\": \"every single legal avenue\", \"from\": 4916, \"to\": 4941}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During the first half of 2024, Lindo and his family faced two successive deportation scares.\", \"from\": 5024, \"to\": 5116, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first half\", \"from\": 5031, \"to\": 5045}, {\"ngram\": \"Lindo\", \"from\": 5055, \"to\": 5060}, {\"ngram\": \"his family\", \"from\": 5065, \"to\": 5075}, {\"ngram\": \"two successive deportation scares\", \"from\": 5082, \"to\": 5115}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The most recent came after their application to remain in Canada on \\\"humanitarian and compassionate grounds\\\" was denied.\", \"from\": 5117, \"to\": 5237, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5175, \"end\": 5181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999999994552127, \"rank\": 5.422599372110048e-10, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their application\", \"from\": 5144, \"to\": 5161}, {\"ngram\": \"humanitarian and compassionate grounds\", \"from\": 5186, \"to\": 5224}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The stress made Lindo lose a considerable amount of weight, and he credits the anxiety with hampering his ability to focus on hurdling.\", \"from\": 5239, \"to\": 5374, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The stress\", \"from\": 5239, \"to\": 5249}, {\"ngram\": \"Lindo\", \"from\": 5255, \"to\": 5260}, {\"ngram\": \"a considerable amount\", \"from\": 5266, \"to\": 5287}, {\"ngram\": \"weight\", \"from\": 5291, \"to\": 5297}, {\"ngram\": \"the anxiety\", \"from\": 5314, \"to\": 5325}, {\"ngram\": \"his ability\", \"from\": 5341, \"to\": 5352}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Being an athlete is hard enough,\\\" said Lindo.\", \"from\": 5376, \"to\": 5422, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 5383, \"to\": 5393}, {\"ngram\": \"Lindo\", \"from\": 5416, \"to\": 5421}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Having to also go through all of this?\", \"from\": 5423, \"to\": 5462, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is a lot on my plate.\\\"\", \"from\": 5463, \"to\": 5491, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 5472, \"to\": 5477}, {\"ngram\": \"my plate\", \"from\": 5481, \"to\": 5489}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But immigration advocates say Lindo is not alone.\", \"from\": 5493, \"to\": 5542, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"immigration advocates\", \"from\": 5497, \"to\": 5518}, {\"ngram\": \"Lindo\", \"from\": 5523, \"to\": 5528}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While the Canadian government acknowledges there are \\\"no accurate figures\\\" for the number of undocumented people in Canada, it estimates the population could range anywhere from 20,000 to 500,000.\", \"from\": 5543, \"to\": 5739, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5553, \"end\": 5572, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_Canada\", \"score\": 0.9905979746581696, \"rank\": 0.009491262408638087, \"text\": \"Canadian government\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_Canada\"}, {\"begin\": 5659, \"end\": 5665, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999999994552127, \"rank\": 5.422599372110048e-10, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"no accurate figures\", \"from\": 5596, \"to\": 5616}, {\"ngram\": \"the number\", \"from\": 5622, \"to\": 5632}, {\"ngram\": \"undocumented people\", \"from\": 5636, \"to\": 5655}, {\"ngram\": \"the population\", \"from\": 5680, \"to\": 5694}]}, {\"s