tp://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999999994552127, \"rank\": 5.422599372110048e-10, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Their visas\", \"from\": 6081, \"to\": 6092}, {\"ngram\": \"their application\", \"from\": 6110, \"to\": 6127}, {\"ngram\": \"a precarious choice\", \"from\": 6165, \"to\": 6184}, {\"ngram\": \"the proper paperwork\", \"from\": 6227, \"to\": 6247}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Syed Hussan, the executive director of Canada's Migrant Workers Alliance for Change (MWAC), said 2023 saw the highest number of deportations in a decade.\", \"from\": 6250, \"to\": 6403, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6289, \"end\": 6295, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999999994552127, \"rank\": 5.422599372110048e-10, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hussan\", \"from\": 6255, \"to\": 6261}, {\"ngram\": \"the executive director\", \"from\": 6263, \"to\": 6285}, {\"ngram\": \"Change\", \"from\": 6327, \"to\": 6333}, {\"ngram\": \"MWAC\", \"from\": 6335, \"to\": 6339}, {\"ngram\": \"the highest number\", \"from\": 6356, \"to\": 6374}, {\"ngram\": \"deportations\", \"from\": 6378, \"to\": 6390}, {\"ngram\": \"a decade\", \"from\": 6394, \"to\": 6402}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He estimates that 40 happen each day.\", \"from\": 6404, \"to\": 6441, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His group has been advocating on Lindo's behalf, in the hopes of preventing his deportation.\", \"from\": 6443, \"to\": 6535, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His group\", \"from\": 6443, \"to\": 6452}, {\"ngram\": \"Lindo's behalf\", \"from\": 6476, \"to\": 6490}, {\"ngram\": \"the hopes\", \"from\": 6495, \"to\": 6504}, {\"ngram\": \"his deportation\", \"from\": 6519, \"to\": 6534}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since December 2021, Canadian Prime Minister Justin Trudeau has promised to implement a regularisation programme that would allow undocumented people to gain legal residency.\", \"from\": 6537, \"to\": 6711, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6558, \"end\": 6581, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999752624448108, \"rank\": 2.473816701510975e-05, \"text\": \"Canadian Prime Minister\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prime_Minister_of_Canada\"}, {\"begin\": 6582, \"end\": 6596, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Trudeau\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Justin Trudeau\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Trudeau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Trudeau\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"December\", \"from\": 6543, \"to\": 6551}, {\"ngram\": \"a regularisation programme\", \"from\": 6623, \"to\": 6649}, {\"ngram\": \"undocumented people\", \"from\": 6667, \"to\": 6686}, {\"ngram\": \"legal residency\", \"from\": 6695, \"to\": 6710}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Hassan points out that such a pathway has yet to materialise.\", \"from\": 6713, \"to\": 6778, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6717, \"end\": 6723, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\", \"score\": 0.9948751749598859, \"rank\": 0.0051512235206562906, \"text\": \"Hassan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such a pathway\", \"from\": 6740, \"to\": 6754}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Trudeau himself has admitted there is no official timeline yet for its creation and implementation.\", \"from\": 6779, \"to\": 6878, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6779, \"end\": 678