ce were fraught.\", \"from\": 7893, \"to\": 7941, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the final days\", \"from\": 7897, \"to\": 7911}, {\"ngram\": \"his race\", \"from\": 7919, \"to\": 7927}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On June 28, he received a call from a private number.\", \"from\": 7942, \"to\": 7995, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 7945, \"to\": 7949}, {\"ngram\": \"a call\", \"from\": 7966, \"to\": 7972}, {\"ngram\": \"a private number\", \"from\": 7978, \"to\": 7994}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The caller identified themselves as an officer with the Canada Border Services Agency.\", \"from\": 7997, \"to\": 8083, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8053, \"end\": 8082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_Border_Services_Agency\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Canada Border Services Agency\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_Border_Services_Agency\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_Border_Services_Agency\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The caller\", \"from\": 7997, \"to\": 8007}, {\"ngram\": \"an officer\", \"from\": 8033, \"to\": 8043}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He announced that Lindo's deportation date had been set for July 10 - less than three weeks before the Paris Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 8084, \"to\": 8207, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lindo's deportation date\", \"from\": 8102, \"to\": 8126}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 8144, \"to\": 8148}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympic Games\", \"from\": 8183, \"to\": 8206}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That evening, the National Hurricane Center in the United States also announced it was tracking a tropical depression that was expected to develop into a hurricane.\", \"from\": 8209, \"to\": 8373, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8227, \"end\": 8252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hurricane_Center\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"National Hurricane Center\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hurricane_Center\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hurricane_Center\"}, {\"begin\": 8260, \"end\": 8273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9880730924635959, \"rank\": 0.012070875739588774, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a tropical depression\", \"from\": 8305, \"to\": 8326}, {\"ngram\": \"a hurricane\", \"from\": 8361, \"to\": 8372}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was headed straight for Jamaica.\", \"from\": 8374, \"to\": 8409, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8401, \"end\": 8408, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.704300704582667e-16, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lindo's recollection of that day remains hazy.\", \"from\": 8411, \"to\": 8457, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lindo's recollection\", \"from\": 8411, \"to\": 8431}, {\"ngram\": \"that day\", \"from\": 8435, \"to\": 8443}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said he arrived for morning practice in a daze and struggled to stay focused.\", \"from\": 8458, \"to\": 8538, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"morning practice\", \"from\": 8481, \"to\": 8497}, {\"ngram\": \"a daze\", \"from\": 8501, \"to\": 8507}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rather than soaring over the hurdles, he knocked several down.\", \"from\": 8539, \"to\": 8601, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the hurdles\", \"from\": 8564, \"to\": 8575}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am going against the hurdles, and I am hitting them pretty bad, the worst way I hit them all year,\\\" said Lindo.\", \"from\": 8603, \"to\": 8717, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the hurdles\", \"from\": 8623, \"to\": 8634}, {\"ngram\": \"Lindo\", \"from\": 8711, \"to\": 8716}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The news of his impending deportation had shaken his resolve.\", \"from\": 8719, \"to\": 8780, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The news\", \"from\": 8719, \"to\": 8727}, {\"ngram\": \"his impending deportation\", \"from\": 8731, \"to\": 8756}, {\"ngram\": \"his resolve\", \"from\": 8768, \"to\": 8779}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As soon as he left practice and returned to his hotel room, Lindo said he broke down.\", \"from\": 8781, \"to\": 8866, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"practice\", \"from\": 8800, \"to\": 8808}, {\"ngram\": \"his hotel room\", \"from\": 8825, \"to\": 8839}, {\"ngram\": \"Lindo\", \"from\": 8841, \"to\": 8846}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The only solace he could find was the hope that if he performed well at the Olympic qualifiers, maybe it could force the Canadian immigration agency to reconsider its decision.\", \"from\": 8868, \"to\": 9044, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8989, \"end\": 8997, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9998285713881555, \"rank\": 0.0001714580042397662, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The only solace\", \"from\": 8868, \"to\": 8883}, {\"ngram\": \"the hope\", \"from\": 8902, \"to\": 8910}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic qualifiers\", \"from\": 8940, \"to\": 8962}, {\"ngram\": \"its decision\", \"from\": 9031, \"to\": 9043}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He cried himself to sleep.\", \"from\": 9045, \"to\": 9071, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The next day, at the Olympic trials, Lindo tried to corral his thoughts - but his knees were beginning to quake.\", \"from\": 9073, \"to\": 9185, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic trials\", \"from\": 9090, \"to\": 9108}, {\"ngram\": \"Lindo\", \"from\": 9110, \"to\": 9115}, {\"ngram\": \"his thoughts\", \"from\": 9132, \"to\": 9144}, {\"ngram\": \"his knees\", \"from\": 9151, \"to\": 9160}, {\"ngram\": \"quake\", \"from\": 9179, \"to\": 9184}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Any moment now, the starting pistol would fire.\", \"from\": 9186, \"to\": 9233, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the starting pistol\", \"from\": 9202, \"to\": 9221}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Suddenly, a referee called a delay from across the track.\", \"from\": 9235, \"to\": 9292, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a referee\", \"from\": 9245, \"to\": 9254}, {\"ngram\": \"a delay\", \"from\": 9262, \"to\": 9269}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 9282, \"to\": 9291}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It gave Lindo five extra seconds - five seconds to pull himself together.\", \"from\": 9293, \"to\": 9366, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lindo\", \"from\": 9301, \"to\": 9306}, {\"ngram\": \"five extra seconds\", \"from\": 9307, \"to\": 9325}, {\"ngram\": \"five seconds\", \"from\": 9328, \"to\": 9340}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He fell to his knees, made the sign of the cross on his chest and asked God to be with him.\", \"from\": 9367, \"to\": 9458, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his knees\", \"from\": 9378, \"to\": 9387}, {\"ngram\": \"the sign\", \"from\": 9394, \"to\": 9402}, {\"ngram\": \"the cross\", \"from\": 9406, \"to\": 9415}, {\"ngram\": \"his chest\", \"from\": 9419, \"to\": 9428}, {\"ngram\": \"God\", \"from\": 9439, \"to\": 9442}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then, with a pop of the gun, he was off.\", \"from\": 9460, \"to\": 9500, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a pop\", \"from\": 9471, \"to\": 9476}, {\"ngram\": \"the gun\", \"from\": 9480, \"to\": 9487}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The race was the exact thing that Aidan Simardone needed.\", \"from\": 9504, \"to\": 9561, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The race\", \"from\": 9504, \"to\": 9512}, {\"ngram\": \"the exact thing\", \"from\": 9517, \"to\": 9532}, {\"ngram\": \"Aidan Simardone\", \"from\": 9538, \"to\": 9553}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As an immigration lawyer for the Lindo family since March, Simardone had been searching for a way to generate the kind of immense public pressure that would force Canada's minister of immigration to intervene.\", \"from\": 9563, \"to\": 9772, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9726, \"end\": 9732, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999999994552127, \"rank\": 5.422599372110048e-10, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an immigration lawyer\", \"from\": 9566, \"to\": 9587}, {\"ngram\": \"the Lindo family\", \"from\": 9592, \"to\": 9608}, {\"ngram\": \"March\", \"from\": 9615, \"to\": 9620}, {\"ngram\": \"Simardone\", \"from\": 9622, \"to\": 9631}, {\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 9655, \"to\": 9660}, {\"ngram\": \"the kind\", \"from\": 9673, \"to\": 9681}, {\"ngram\": \"immense public pressure\", \"from\": 9685, \"to\": 9708}, {\"ngram\": \"immigration\", \"from\": 9747, \"to\": 9758}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Simardone, who represents the family pro bono, felt the only recourse to prevent Lindo's deportation was to appeal for a temporary resident permit (TRP).\", \"from\": 9774, \"to\": 9927, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9922, \"end\": 9925, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Audience_measurement\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.137165599636117e-15, \"text\": \"TRP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Audience_measurement\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Audience_measurement\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Simardone\", \"from\": 9774, \"to\": 9783}, {\"ngram\": \"the only recourse\", \"from\": 9826, \"to\": 9843}, {\"ngram\": \"Lindo's deportation\", \"from\": 9855, \"to\": 9874}, {\"ngram\": \"a temporary resident permit\", \"from\": 9893, \"to\": 9920}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even people otherwise deemed \\\"inadmissible\\\" to Canada can be eligible to receive such a permit.\", \"from\": 9928, \"to\": 10023, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9975, \"end\": 9981, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999999994552127, \"rank\": 5.422599372110048e-10, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Even people\", \"from\": 9928, \"to\": 9939}, {\"ngram\": \"such a permit\", \"from\": 10009, \"to\": 10022}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Simardone had contacted Nicole Noworyta, a social media strategist, to help organise a public outreach campaign.\", \"from\": 10025, \"to\": 10137, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Simardone\", \"from\": 10025, \"to\": 10034}, {\"ngram\": \"Nicole Noworyta\", \"from\": 10049, \"to\": 10064}, {\"ngram\": \"a social media strategist\", \"from\": 10066, \"to\": 10091}, {\"ngram\": \"a public outreach campaign\", \"from\": 10110, \"to\": 10136}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Together, they prepared social media content and petitions, bringing together a community of local activists.\", \"from\": 10138, \"to\": 10247, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"social media content\", \"from\": 10162, \"to\": 10182}, {\"ngram\": \"petitions\", \"from\": 10187, \"to\": 10196}, {\"ngram\": \"a community\", \"from\": 10216, \"to\": 10227}, {\"ngram\": \"local activists\", \"from\": 10231, \"to\": 10246}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Me and Aidan were leading the effort, but we had around 200 people mobilised,\\\" said Noworyta.\", \"from\": 10249, \"to\": 10343, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Aidan\", \"from\": 10257, \"to\": 10262}, {\"ngram\": \"the effort\", \"from\": 10276, \"to\": 10286}, {\"ngram\": \"around 200 people\", \"from\": 10299, \"to\": 10316}, {\"ngram\": \"Noworyta\", \"from\": 10334, \"to\": 10342}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The only thing they needed was a spectacle big enough to draw the public eye.\", \"from\": 10345, \"to\": 10422, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The only thing\", \"from\": 10345, \"to\": 10359}, {\"ngram\": \"a spectacle\", \"from\": 10376, \"to\": 10387}, {\"ngram\": \"the public eye\", \"from\": 10407, \"to\": 10421}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And Lindo's race would be just the ticket.\", \"from\": 10423, \"to\": 10465, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lindo's race\", \"from\": 10427, \"to\": 10439}, {\"ngram\": \"just the ticket\", \"from\": 10449, \"to\": 10464}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the Olympic trials, he cleared the first two hurdles with ease.\", \"from\": 10467, \"to\": 10533, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic trials\", \"from\": 10470, \"to\": 10488}, {\"ngram\": \"the first two hurdles\", \"from\": 10501, \"to\": 10522}, {\"ngram\": \"ease\", \"from\": 10528, \"to\": 10532}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, on the third hurdle, his right leg - his dominant leg - grazed the crossbar, slowing him down.\", \"from\": 10534, \"to\": 10637, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the third hurdle\", \"from\": 10546, \"to\": 10562}, {\"ngram\": \"his right leg\", \"from\": 10564, \"to\": 10577}, {\"ngram\": \"his dominant leg\", \"from\": 10580, \"to\": 10596}, {\"ngram\": \"the crossbar\", \"from\": 10606, \"to\": 10618}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He drifted to the back of the heat.\", \"from\": 10638, \"to\": 10673, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the back\", \"from\": 10652, \"to\": 10660}, {\"ngram\": \"the heat\", \"from\": 10664, \"to\": 10672}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But in a sport where the final results come down to split seconds, Lindo knew better than to give up.\", \"from\": 10675, \"to\": 10776, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sport\", \"from\": 10682, \"to\": 10689}, {\"ngram\": \"the final results\", \"from\": 10696, \"to\": 10713}, {\"ngram\": \"seconds\", \"from\": 10733, \"to\": 10740}, {\"ngram\": \"Lindo\", \"from\": 10742, \"to\": 10747}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With each subsequent hurdle he cleared, Lindo gained ground, and in the final stretch, he closed the gap, clinching third place by one-fiftieth of a second.\", \"from\": 10778, \"to\": 10934, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"each subsequent hurdle\", \"from\": 10783, \"to\": 10805}, {\"ngram\": \"Lindo\", \"from\": 10818, \"to\": 10823}, {\"ngram\": \"ground\", \"from\": 10831, \"to\": 10837}, {\"ngram\": \"the final stretch\", \"from\": 10846, \"to\": 10863}, {\"ngram\": \"the gap\", \"from\": 10875, \"to\": 10882}, {\"ngram\": \"third place\", \"from\": 10894, \"to\": 10905}, {\"ngram\": \"one-fiftieth\", \"from\": 10909, \"to\": 10921}, {\"ngram\": \"a second\", \"from\": 10925, \"to\": 10933}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the first time, Lindo stood on a national podium as a champion, waving the flag of his home province with pride.\", \"from\": 10936, \"to\": 11052, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 10940, \"to\": 10954}, {\"ngram\": \"Lindo\", \"from\": 10956, \"to\": 10961}, {\"ngram\": \"a national podium\", \"from\": 10971, \"to\": 10988}, {\"ngram\": \"a champion\", \"from\": 10992, \"to\": 11002}, {\"ngram\": \"the flag\", \"from\": 11011, \"to\": 11019}, {\"ngram\": \"his home province\", \"from\": 11023, \"to\": 11040}, {\"ngram\": \"pride\", \"from\": 11046, \"to\": 11051}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the race, news of the Olympic prospect facing imminent deportation spread rapidly on social media.\", \"from\": 11056, \"to\": 11160, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 11062, \"to\": 11070}, {\"ngram\": \"news\", \"from\": 11072, \"to\": 11076}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic prospect\", \"from\": 11080, \"to\": 11100}, {\"ngram\": \"imminent deportation\", \"from\": 11108, \"to\": 11128}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 11147, \"to\": 11159}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Petitions to defer Lindo's deportation were receiving thousands of signatures daily.\", \"from\": 11161, \"to\": 11245, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Petitions\", \"from\": 11161, \"to\": 11170}, {\"ngram\": \"Lindo's deportation\", \"from\": 11180, \"to\": 11199}, {\"ngram\": \"thousands\", \"from\": 11215, \"to\": 11224}, {\"ngram\": \"signatures\", \"from\": 11228, \"to\": 11238}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At first, Simardone said it looked like the immigration officials would refuse to budge.\", \"from\": 11247, \"to\": 11335, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Simardone\", \"from\": 11257, \"to\": 11266}, {\"ngram\": \"the immigration officials\", \"from\": 11287, \"to\": 11312}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But then he got good news: Canada's immigration agency had issued Lindo's family a one-year temporary resident permit.\", \"from\": 11337, \"to\": 11455, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11364, \"end\": 11370, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999999994552127, \"rank\": 5.422599372110048e-10, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"good news\", \"from\": 11353, \"to\": 11362}, {\"ngram\": \"Lindo's family\", \"from\": 11403, \"to\": 11417}, {\"ngram\": \"a one-year temporary resident permit\", \"from\": 11418, \"to\": 11454}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Simardone admits he \\\"burst into tears\\\".\", \"from\": 11456, \"to\": 11495, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Simardone\", \"from\": 11456, \"to\": 11465}, {\"ngram\": \"tears\", \"from\": 11488, \"to\": 11493}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lindo and his family are currently waiting for a judicial review of their application to stay in Canada on \\\"humanitarian and compassionate grounds\\\".\", \"from\": 